    • onExistingOrNewCoverage

      public B onExistingOrNewCoverage()
      Sets the Coverage on the generated CovTerm as follows: if a coverage is specified via onCoverage or by using coverageBuilder.withCovTerm() then use the specified Coverage. Otherwise a new ui ready WC med PolicyCoverage is created (see PolicyCoverageBuilder.uiReadyWCMedCoverage(gw.api.financials.CurrencyAmount, gw.api.financials.CurrencyAmount) for details about creating a claim to use with the resulting policy.)
      Returns:
      the modified builder
